doctype
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title NodeBird 로그인
    style.
      .input-group label {
        width: 200px;
        display: inline-block;
      }
  body
    form#login-form(action='/auth/join' method='post')
        h2 NodeBird 회원가입 페이지.
        .input-group
            label(for='email') 이메일
            input#email(type='email' name='email' required autofocus)
        .input-group
            label(for='nick') 닉네임
            input#password(type='text' name='nick' required)
        .input-group
            label(for='password') 비밀번호
            input#password(type='password' name='password' required)
        if joinError
            .error-message= joinError
        a(href='/'): button#join(type='button') 메인페이지 이동
        button#login(type='submit') 회원가입
